      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
        <div class="space-y-6">
          <p class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.28em] text-secondary/90">
            <span class="inline-block w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-secondary"></span>
            Verified stays, transparent pricing
          </p>
          <h1 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-bold leading-tight">
            Book your next stay with confidence.<br>
            Trusted hotels and homes for every journey.
          </h1>
          <p class="text-lg lg:text-xl text-gray-200 max-w-xl">
            HotStay makes travel simple with curated stays, flexible plans, and support that is ready whenever you need it.
          </p>
          <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4">
            <a href="/Hot-Stay/home" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center bg-secondary hover:bg-secondary/90 text-white font-semibold px-6 py-3 rounded-md transition-colors">
              Explore stays
            </a>
            <a href="#how-it-works" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center text-white/90 hover:text-white border border-white/20 px-6 py-3 rounded-md transition-colors">
