            <div class="rounded-3xl border border-white/15 bg-white/10 p-5 backdrop-blur-xl shadow-2xl">
              <p class="text-sm uppercase tracking-[0.24em] text-gray-200/70">Verified</p>
              <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-3">Trusted properties</h3>
              <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-gray-200/80">Quality stays vetted by our team for safety and clean amenities.</p>
