        <div>
          <p class="text-sm uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-secondary font-semibold">Explore styles</p>
          <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold mt-3 text-text">Browse curated stay themes</h2>
        </div>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 max-w-xl">Swipe through trending categories and jump into the vibe that fits your next trip.</p>
