          <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-full border border-gray-200 bg-white px-4 py-3 text-sm font-medium text-text shadow-sm">🏖️ Beachfront</span>
          <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-full border border-gray-200 bg-white px-4 py-3 text-sm font-medium text-text shadow-sm">🏔️ Amazing views</span>
          <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-full border border-gray-200 bg-white px-4 py-3 text-sm font-medium text-text shadow-sm">🔥 Trending</span>
          <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-full border border-gray-200 bg-white px-4 py-3 text-sm font-medium text-text shadow-sm">🎨 Design</span>
          <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-full border border-gray-200 bg-white px-4 py-3 text-sm font-medium text-text shadow-sm">⛳ Golfing</span>
          <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-full border border-gray-200 bg-white px-4 py-3 text-sm font-medium text-text shadow-sm">🍷 Vineyards</span>
          <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-full border border-gray-200 bg-white px-4 py-3 text-sm font-medium text-text shadow-sm">❄️ Arctic</span>
          <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-full border border-gray-200 bg-white px-4 py-3 text-sm font-medium text-text shadow-sm">🌵 Desert</span>
        </div>
