          <div class="p-6">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">Mountain lodges</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Cozy cabins and lodges for nature lovers and weekend adventures.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="overflow-hidden rounded-3xl border border-gray-200 bg-white shadow-sm hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow">
